-- MOVES-BNY Mellon makes senior appointment in wealth management unit
-- 
-- Wed Sep 17, 2014 10:48AM EDT
-- None



Sept 17 (Reuters) - Bank of New York Mellon Corp <BK.N> said it hired Gary Cindrich as wealth director for business development in its wealth management unit.

Cindrich will join BNY Mellon Wealth Management's Pittsburgh office. He joins from Virtual OfficeWare, where he was partner and senior vice-president of sales.